data.description: Beautifully Renovated 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom Townhome in Fort Caroline Lakes, featuring No HOA Fee. Newer Roof and HVAC system, along with a fully updated Kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances. Fresh countertops and sinks in the bathrooms, complemented by new vinyl wood plank flooring throughout. The home has been completely replumbed and recently painted both inside and out. Enjoy the cozy dining area. The fenced backyard offers ample privacy and space for gatherings. Conveniently located near shopping centers, 295, Town Center, Beaches, and just a 15-minute drive to Naval Base. Welcome to your new home!
